item.title: About
item.description: Hello everyone! I am SenlinOS, use GNU/Linux to make comics. My Projects: SLOS-GIMPainter (Brush package for GIMP): GitHub. Do Not Update MyPaintBrushes-GIMP (Brushes): GitHub. (No need to update) Homepage: SenlinOS.com Mirror Site: senlinos.github.io | senlinos.gitlab.io Expand to view SenlinOS.com QRcode Desktop OS: Trisquel GNU/Linux、 Laptop OS: Debian (Live Xfce iso) Software: AzPainter-V3 (Digital Line art)、GIMP+GMIC (Coloring & Making)、Blender (Video editing & 3D model) My PGP Public Key: SenlinOS-PGP.
